---

This image bundles the official Claude Code CLI
(``@anthropic-ai/claude-code``) from npm. Claude Code itself is Anthropic
software; see the package's own LICENSE.md for its terms and
https://anthropic.com/legal for Anthropic's consumer/commercial terms of
service.

Intended for personal, single-user operation. Authentication flows in this
image use Anthropic's published OAuth client id and endpoints (same as the
official CLI's interactive flow) — they are NOT a workaround for the
prohibition on routing Free/Pro/Max subscription credentials through third-
party products on behalf of other users. Using this image to serve other
users with one's own Claude subscription is not supported and may violate
Anthropic's terms.
